'''''Tekra Point''''' was a [[Colony ship/Legends|colony ship]] once in the service of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. When agents of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] stole the vehicle, they remodeled it to serve as a drop-off point for the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Chenlambec]], who would often rescue high-risk Rebel sympathizers, such as [[Agapos the Ninth]].

